WEBVTT

00:01:29.056 --> 00:01:31.440
The answer is no, no and no.

00:01:31.440 --> 00:01:33.113
A sandwich can be delicious,

00:01:33.113 --> 00:01:35.415
that parking space can be nearby,

00:01:35.415 --> 00:01:38.155
and that game can be a blowout,

00:01:38.155 --> 00:01:42.380
but not everything can be awesome.

00:01:42.380 --> 00:01:44.010
(Laughter)

00:01:44.010 --> 00:01:45.659
So when you use the word "awesome"

00:01:45.659 --> 00:01:48.977
to describe the most mundane of things,

00:01:48.977 --> 00:01:51.880
you're taking away the very power of the word.

00:01:51.880 --> 00:01:54.298
This author says, "Snowy days

00:01:54.298 --> 00:01:58.573
or finding money in your pants is awesome."

00:01:58.573 --> 00:01:59.451
(Laughter)

00:01:59.451 --> 00:02:01.433
Um, no, it is not,